dc_title_s: Bike Paths City of Madison, WI 2023
dc_description_s: This data layer represents bike paths for the City of Madison and Dane County, Wisconsin in 2023. [Bike Paths. Generally crushed stone within rural areas; paved in urban areas. Includes paths that can accommodate biking, but does not include pedestrian paths. This data layer is used by the Dane County Bicycle Map and Neighborhood Development Plan Resource Viewer applications.]
dc_creator_sm: City of Madison - Metropolitan Planning Organization (MPO)
uw_supplemental_s: Archived dataset at UW-Madison. For the most current version of this data please visit: https://data-cityofmadison.opendata.arcgis.com/
